<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground">엑셀 파일 업로드</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
      AI 기반 오류 검출 및 수정을 위해 엑셀 파일을 업로드하세요.
    </p>
  </div>

  <%= render Ui::CardComponent.new do %>
    <%= form_with url: excel_files_path, local: true, html: { multipart: true } do |form| %>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-foreground">
            파일 업로드
          </label>
          <div class="mt-1 flex justify-center px-6 pt-5 pb-6 border-2 border-border border-dashed rounded-md">
            <div class="space-y-1 text-center">
              <svg class="mx-auto h-12 w-12 text-muted-foreground" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 48 48">
                <path d="M28 8H12a4 4 0 00-4 4v20m32-12v8m0 0v8a4 4 0 01-4 4H12a4 4 0 01-4-4v-4m32-4l-3.172-3.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0L28 28M8 32l9.172-9.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L28 28m0 0l4 4m4-24h8m-4-4v8m-12 4h.02" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              </svg>
              <div class="flex text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                <label for="file-upload" class="relative cursor-pointer bg-background rounded-md font-medium text-primary hover:text-primary/80 focus-within:outline-none focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-offset-2 focus-within:ring-ring">
                  <span>파일 선택</span>
                  <%= form.file_field :file, id: "file-upload", class: "sr-only", required: true,
                      accept: ".xlsx,.xls,.csv,.xlsm" %>
                </label>
                <p class="pl-1">또는 드래그 앤 드롭</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                XLSX, XLS, CSV 최대 50MB
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-primary/10 p-4 rounded-md">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">
                분석 항목
              </h3>
              <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-primary/80">
                <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
                  <li>수식 오류 및 순환 참조</li>
                  <li>데이터 유효성 검사 문제</li>
                  <li>서식 일관성 문제</li>
                  <li>누락된 또는 잘못된 데이터</li>
                  <li>성능 최적화 기회</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-warning/10 p-4 rounded-md">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-warning" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-warning">
                크레딧 사용
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-warning/80">
                파일 복잡도에 따라 약 10-50 크레딧이 사용됩니다.
                현재 <strong><%= current_user.credits %> 크레딧</strong>을 보유하고 있습니다.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-between">
          <%= link_to "취소", excel_files_path, 
              class: "inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-input shadow-sm text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-foreground bg-background hover:bg-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-ring" %>
          <%= form.submit "업로드 및 분석", 
              class: "inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-primary-foreground bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-ring" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
</div>